Ambassador Wilson, Niger or yellowcake.

791
00:59:03,346 --> 00:59:06,370
Tell Karl I'll be in my office
straight after I'm done.

792
00:59:11,688 --> 00:59:13,774
The 5th US Circuit Court of Appeals...

793
00:59:13,878 --> 00:59:15,755
This has become a trust issue
