797
00:59:22,637 --> 00:59:23,993
Who is Joe Wilson?

798
00:59:24,931 --> 00:59:28,268
A new controversy over re-targeting
some of America's nuclear weapons.

799
00:59:28,164 --> 00:59:29,937
There will be more
at the President's press conference.

800
00:59:33,065 --> 00:59:34,212
David?

801
00:59:34,212 --> 00:59:37,549
If someone works at the CIA
and they sent their spouse on a trip,

802
00:59:38,696 --> 00:59:40,573
would there be a paper trail?

803
00:59:41,407 --> 00:59:44,744
Any such request would require approval
from the chain of command.

804
00:59:46,309 --> 00:59:49,437
From the requestor
right up to the Director of Operations.

805
00:59:49,437 --> 00:59:51,940
Yes, paperwork
would normally be generated.

806
00:59:53,087 --> 00:59:54,338
Okay.

807
00:59:56,736 --> 00:59:59,865
Does the President
have the power to declassify information?

808
01:00:19,261 --> 01:00:20,512
Valerie?

809
