814
01:00:43,557 --> 01:00:44,913
He just went ahead and did it.

815
01:00:46,060 --> 01:00:47,624
Does this run overseas?

816
01:00:47,624 --> 01:00:49,501
It's in the newspaper, Valerie.
It's on the news.

817
01:00:49,501 --> 01:00:52,525
Novak's column. Is he syndicated overseas?

818
01:00:52,421 --> 01:00:53,777
It's everywhere.

819
01:00:56,384 --> 01:00:57,427
God.

820
01:01:19,012 --> 01:01:20,785
Jessica McDowell.
Maureen McDermont.

821
01:01:20,785 --> 01:01:22,871
- I just flew in from Scotland.
- Valerie, what do you do?

822
01:01:22,871 --> 01:01:25,686
I work in venture capital.

823
01:01:25,686 --> 01:01:27,563
Grace Semel. Sigma Chemicals.

824
01:01:27,563 --> 01:01:30,170
Paris, Milan, Vienna.

825
01:01:30,379 --> 01:01:31,943
Who are you?

826
01:01:31,943 --> 01:01:34,341
We need a matrix of everyone
you've come into contact with

827
01:01:34,341 --> 01:01:37,470
- in a covert capacity.
- I've already started a list.

828
01:01:37,365 --> 01:01:41,119
Good. We need to get an idea, fast,
