829
01:01:41,119 --> 01:01:45,395
Sir, I have several live-ops at crucial stages.
People in the field

830
01:01:45,290 --> 01:01:47,585
- in critical windows of operation.
- One thing at a time.

831
01:01:47,897 --> 01:01:50,922
Make a list, then come back here.
Don't do anything else.

832
01:01:54,780 --> 01:01:56,657
Why is Internal Security here?

833
01:01:57,387 --> 01:02:01,454
To help you and us
conduct this damage assessment.

834
01:02:08,649 --> 01:02:11,360
Ms. Plame? We're going this way.

835
01:02:45,668 --> 01:02:46,815
The restroom.

836
01:02:53,697 --> 01:02:54,844
Ms. Plame?

837
01:02:56,200 --> 01:02:57,347
Ms. Plame?

838
01:03:03,082 --> 01:03:04,334
Ms. Plame?

839
01:03:21,852 --> 01:03:23,729
Val? Val!

840
01:03:24,042 --> 01:03:26,545
Jack, I've got to get a message to Baghdad.

841
01:03:26,441 --> 01:03:29,882
I've got 15 scientists being taken
to the border today.

842
01:03:29,882 --> 01:03:31,655
I have to get word to them.

843
01:03:31,655 --> 01:03:33,010
