844
01:03:33,115 --> 01:03:35,826
Jack, they're packed and ready to go.

845
01:03:36,243 --> 01:03:38,016
You know what this means.

846
01:03:41,040 --> 01:03:43,125
- Sorry. I've got to go.
- Ms. Plame.

847
01:03:44,272 --> 01:03:46,671
Val, can I see you for a minute?

848
01:03:52,510 --> 01:03:54,179
Take a walk.

849
01:03:55,847 --> 01:03:58,767
As of this morning,
all CPD operations involving you

850
01:03:58,767 --> 01:04:00,018
