853
01:04:04,502 --> 01:04:08,361
Any further involvement in operations
is no longer possible.

854
01:04:09,091 --> 01:04:11,802
Bill, I have eight, nine teams in the field.

855
01:04:11,802 --> 01:04:15,556
We have assets
in Kuala Lumpur, Mumbai, Dubai.

856
01:04:26,505 --> 01:04:28,799
I need to brief my replacement
in the Joint Task Force.

857
01:04:29,008 --> 01:04:31,198
The head of the JTFI's identity is classified

858
01:04:31,198 --> 01:04:35,682
- for reasons of operational security.
- I have a critical operation

859
