866
01:05:20,104 --> 01:05:24,067
This comes from the Vice President,
the Chief of Staff, or a top advisor.

867
01:05:23,963 --> 01:05:25,110
I got to go.

868
01:05:25,110 --> 01:05:26,361
- Look at my picture.
- I will.

869
01:05:26,778 --> 01:05:29,385
Trevor won't let me
borrow his Power Ranger.

870
01:05:30,011 --> 01:05:32,931
- Mommy!
- Did you say please?

871
01:05:32,931 --> 01:05:35,329
- I said please!
- There's a 1982 act

872
01:05:35,225 --> 01:05:37,728
