Look, I can't talk right now.

883
01:06:07,864 --> 01:06:09,845
- Well, I can't make a comment.
- Mom!

884
01:06:10,158 --> 01:06:13,391
Look, I'm going
to call you back tomorrow, okay?

885
01:06:13,287 --> 01:06:14,851
I'm really sorry.

886
01:06:14,955 --> 01:06:17,041
- Oh, my God.
- Shit.

887
01:06:18,083 --> 01:06:19,439
It's got to be true.

888
01:06:25,904 --> 01:06:29,450
Your mom called.
Your uncle. Janey in Chicago.

889
01:06:29,450 --> 01:06:31,744
I wrote it down there for you.

890
01:06:32,161 --> 01:06:34,351
And Andrea Mitchell called.

891
01:06:35,498 --> 01:06:37,375
She said White House sources say

892
01:06:37,479 --> 01:06:42,797
