the day after tomorrow.

896
01:06:51,974 --> 01:06:53,225
No.

897
01:06:54,060 --> 01:06:56,666
You're not going on TV, Joe.

898
01:07:03,340 --> 01:07:04,487
Thank you.

899
01:07:07,303 --> 01:07:10,744
This was clearly designed
