their own family's name

904
01:07:21,485 --> 01:07:24,613
dragged through this particular mud.

905
01:07:33,790 --> 01:07:39,421
I didn't prepare for this moment.
I had no plan for this day.

906
01:07:39,212 --> 01:07:40,985
When did you join?

907
01:07:41,715 --> 01:07:43,905
'85, straight out of college.

908
01:07:44,948 --> 01:07:47,346
- Wow, that's...
- Eighteen years.

909
01:07:47,346 --> 01:07:49,119
So, did they find you, or...

910
01:07:49,119 --> 01:07:50,996
No, I approached them.

911
01:07:51,726 --> 01:07:54,124
And did Joe know?

912
01:07:54,437 --> 01:07:55,688
Yes.

913
01:07:56,314 --> 01:07:57,669
Your parents?

914
01:07:58,087 --> 01:07:59,859
Yes, but that's all.

915
01:08:02,466 --> 01:08:05,490
So, do you have lovers all over the world?

916
01:08:05,803 --> 01:08:07,263
Do you have a gun?

917
01:08:07,472 --> 01:08:09,453
Have you killed people?

918
01:08:10,809 --> 01:08:12,269
I can't. I...

919
01:08:14,146 --> 01:08:16,231
I can't tell you anything.

920
01:08:19,151 --> 01:08:21,341
You can't tell me anything.

921
01:08:21,862 --> 01:08:23,322
Okay. All right.

922
01:08:23,948 --> 01:08:27,285
So, do you want to go shopping?

923
01:08:27,180 --> 01:08:29,579
- See a movie? Mani-pedi?
- Diana.

924
01:08:44,178 --> 01:08:45,429
Hi, Mom.

925
01:08:49,183 --> 01:08:50,747
Did your wife send you to Niger?

926
01:08:50,747 --> 01:08:53,667
I was not sent by my wife,
but the issue is not who sent me,

927
01:08:53,667 --> 01:08:55,544
it's whether or not a crime was committed.

928
01:08:57,838 --> 01:09:00,862
- I'm going to get it!
- I'm going to get it! I got it!

929
01:09:00,967 --> 01:09:02,218
Hello?

930
01:09:04,304 --> 01:09:05,451
Hello?

931
01:09:05,451 --> 01:09:09,413
Your husband is a communist.
I hope you die, you commie whore.

932
01:09:09,622 --> 01:09:11,707
- We know where you live.
- Who is this?

933
01:09:11,707 --> 01:09:13,480
- Trevor!
- Who...

934
01:09:15,566 --> 01:09:16,713
Beat it!

935
01:09:19,841 --> 01:09:22,344
Mommy, Trevor won't let me go
on his tractor.

936
01:09:22,239 --> 01:09:25,576
Okay. So, find something else to play.
I don't...

937
01:09:27,141 --> 01:09:28,288
Mommy?

938
01:09:29,852 --> 01:09:31,103
Mommy?

939
01:09:31,103 --> 01:09:32,772
What? What?

940
01:09:42,052 --> 01:09:45,181
"He stayed inside for more than two weeks.

941
01:09:46,432 --> 01:09:47,788
"Then he nibbled..."

942
01:10:04,681 --> 01:10:05,932
Zahraa?

943
01:10:06,558 --> 01:10:10,416
Hammad has disappeared.
His wife, his children are missing.

944
01:10:11,042 --> 01:10:14,275
My uncle in Mansour,
he said they were targeting them.

945
01:10:14,275 --> 01:10:15,943
They were killing them.

946
01:10:15,943 --> 01:10:17,924
- Who?
- Hammad's colleagues.

947
01:10:17,924 --> 01:10:22,513
Dr. Habbuk was shot dead in the street.
Dr. Falli was murdered in his hallway.

948
01:10:23,034 --> 01:10:26,162
- Listen...
- I know you can't tell me where he is.

949
01:10:26,058 --> 01:10:28,665
Just tell me you have him.
Please, I beg you.

950
01:10:28,665 --> 01:10:31,168
I don't need to know anything.
Just tell me he's safe.

951
01:10:35,547 --> 01:10:37,216
We don't have him.

952
01:10:40,448 --> 01:10:42,638
You said he would be safe.

953
01:10:44,098 --> 01:10:46,497
You said we would help you.
You promised.

954
01:10:47,331 --> 01:10:48,791
I trusted you.

955
01:10:54,005 --> 01:10:55,986
The Justice Department need to establish

956
01:10:55,986 --> 01:10:59,636
