sought to destroy the career

957
01:10:59,427 --> 01:11:02,973
of a public servant to punish me
for telling the truth.

958
01:11:04,433 --> 01:11:06,935
- What's going on?
- What are you doing here?

959
01:11:16,633 --> 01:11:20,179
Falli. Hubbuk. Who else?

960
01:11:20,804 --> 01:11:21,951
I don't know what you're talking about.

961
01:11:22,056 --> 01:11:24,454
Don't bullshit me. Who else is dead?

962
01:11:25,393 --> 01:11:28,521
You were right.
It was all about the scientists.

963
01:11:28,417 --> 01:11:30,189
