965
01:11:31,441 --> 01:11:35,090
We passed your case files to liaison.
Mossad were already on the same page.

966
01:11:34,986 --> 01:11:36,759
They've been hunting these guys down
since the invasion.

967
01:11:36,759 --> 01:11:39,992
You'll drive them underground.
They'll run straight to Iran. Pakistan.

968
01:11:39,992 --> 01:11:41,243
Valerie, it's not your problem.

969
01:11:41,243 --> 01:11:44,163
- How can you sleep at night?
- I sleep just fine.

970
01:11:45,414 --> 01:11:48,647
Now, Carol's mother is here. I'm sorry,
but I'm going to have to ask you to leave.

971
01:11:48,647 --> 01:11:51,775
It's called counter-proliferation, Jack.

972
01:11:52,505 --> 01:11:53,756
Counter.

973
01:11:56,780 --> 01:11:59,492
Linda, are you still here? It's late.

974
01:12:36,406 --> 01:12:39,326
At the end of the day,
it's of keen interest to me

975
